==English==
===Etymology===
From [[w:Star Trek|Star Trek]] + [[-er]]

===Noun===
'''Trekker''' (''plural'' '''Trekkers''')

#A fan of the [[TV]] [[science fiction]] series ''[[w:Star_Trek|Star Trek]]''.

====Synonyms====
*[[Trekkie]]

====Usage note====
*There is a division between fans over which term - Trekkie or Trekker is appropriate. Most fans - and dictionaries, for that matter - tend to prefer one over the other. Trekkie is generally the more well-known term, however.